rows.label: qst103901_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex! Thank you for the
58,954G! You sent so much!

rows.label: qst103901_msg0002
rows.name:
You always send money...
It's a huge help.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0003
rows.name:
Huh? Correl-obasan, wasn't
it supposed to be 90,000G?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0004
rows.name: No, dear. It was 58,954G, no mistake.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0005
rows.name:
That's almost 30,000G short...
I wonder if someone skimmed it
off the top during delivery?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh my... Do you think
you were swindled?

rows.label: qst103901_msg0007
rows.name:
I did think it was a
rather odd amount...

rows.label: qst103901_msg0010
rows.name:
Come to think of it, when I sent you
that seared Cloud Sea Shark, the
handling fee was absolutely enormous.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0008
rows.name:
Hmm... Looks like we need to
investigate this properly.

rows.label: qst103901_msg0009
rows.name:
I'll go to Avaritia and check
with Maxim-san the courier!
